  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soccer Pro Simulator is a realistic football (soccer) simulation designed to make you feel like a rockstar, making the crowd roar after scoring amazing goals. From powerful midfield shots to spectacular bicycle kicks, experience the thrill of becoming a true legend!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/16aa77d4801cca2fc76bd6bc4dc0bedb.webp?t=1772360979\" width=200 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c65c2526b77c67e386db3a14dbf73ac4.poster.avif?t=1772360979\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c65c2526b77c67e386db3a14dbf73ac4.webm?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c65c2526b77c67e386db3a14dbf73ac4.mp4?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Soccer Pro Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soccer Pro Simulator is a realistic football (soccer) simulation that immerses players in the excitement of the sport. Feel like a rockstar as you celebrate incredible goals, from powerful midfield shots to spectacular bicycle kicks, all powered by a solid physics engine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c59edf086a2b3d1e18432c3aeb76e46f.webp?t=1772360979\" width=275 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/5e71f8413f6215874065ffc9eda1a3fa.poster.avif?t=1772360979\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/5e71f8413f6215874065ffc9eda1a3fa.webm?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/5e71f8413f6215874065ffc9eda1a3fa.mp4?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With singleplayer mode against CPU opponents at varying difficulties and a spectator mode for CPU vs. CPU matches, the game offers engaging gameplay and realistic match scenarios. Refine your skills and strategies to become a true legend on the pitch in this exhilarating soccer experience!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Soccer Pro Simulator is a realistic football (soccer) simulation designed to make you feel like a rockstar, making the crowd roar after scoring amazing goals. From powerful midfield shots to spectacular bicycle kicks, experience the thrill of becoming a true legend!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/16aa77d4801cca2fc76bd6bc4dc0bedb.webp?t=1772360979\" width=200 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c65c2526b77c67e386db3a14dbf73ac4.poster.avif?t=1772360979\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c65c2526b77c67e386db3a14dbf73ac4.webm?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c65c2526b77c67e386db3a14dbf73ac4.mp4?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About Soccer Pro Simulator</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Soccer Pro Simulator is a realistic football (soccer) simulation that immerses players in the excitement of the sport. Feel like a rockstar as you celebrate incredible goals, from powerful midfield shots to spectacular bicycle kicks, all powered by a solid physics engine.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/c59edf086a2b3d1e18432c3aeb76e46f.webp?t=1772360979\" width=275 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/5e71f8413f6215874065ffc9eda1a3fa.poster.avif?t=1772360979\" width=600 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/5e71f8413f6215874065ffc9eda1a3fa.webm?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3284110/extras/5e71f8413f6215874065ffc9eda1a3fa.mp4?t=1772360979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With singleplayer mode against CPU opponents at varying difficulties and a spectator mode for CPU vs. CPU matches, the game offers engaging gameplay and realistic match scenarios. Refine your skills and strategies to become a true legend on the pitch in this exhilarating soccer experience!</p>",
